  • Constructor Details

    • Project

      public Project(int jobNumber, String jobName, String buildType, String physicalAddress, int erfNumber, double totalFee, double totalPaid, LocalDate deadline, Person architect, Person contractor, Person customer, boolean completed)
      Create a project from the information listed
      Parameters:
      jobNumber - the jobs assigned number
      jobName - jobs name
      buildType - the type of building the project is
      physicalAddress - the address of where the project is being constructed
      erfNumber - ERF number (would be UPRN in UK)
      totalFee - total cost of the project
      totalPaid - how much has been paid
      deadline - completion date
      architect - architect of the project
      contractor - contractor building it
      customer - customer for the project
      completed - has the project been completed or not
